<p>Welcome to the The Education Partnership's Lending Library, <%= @name %>!</p>
<% if @password != nil %>
	<p>Your password is: <%= @password %></p>
<% else %>
	<p>After confirming your account, you will need to click the 'Forgot your password?' link and follow the instructions to create a new password for your account before you can sign in.</p>
<% end %>
<p>You can confirm your account email through the link below:</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Confirm my account', confirmation_url(@resource, confirmation_token: @token) %></p>
